Line 418 of emboss/embossversion.c is simply printing the value of _FORTIFY_SOURCE which may have some strange definition on your system.

Try replacing line 418 with: 

      ajFmtPrintF(outfile, "_FORTIFY_SOURCE defined\n");

and it should be fine …
